en.title: FusionExcel Sponsored Selangor Football Team Malaysian Champions!
en.content:
MESSAGE OF APPRECIATION FROM ZAKARIA AB RAHIM, SELANGOR FOOTBALL TEAM MANAGER. 

Selangor Football Team now Malaysian Champions! We won 6-1 last night. We also won the TREBLE Championship Crown - The Charity Cup, The F.A.Cup and the Super League Cup! Thank you very much to FusionExcel for all your support. FusionExcel is part of our success. We really appreciate it! 

Zakaria Ab Rahim, Selangor Team Manager.
